<plot>Lakshman Prasad and Prem Amar Tripathi are residents of Uttar Pradesh who are anxious to meet girls and get married. They consult a astrologer, who instructs them to re-locate to a city that starts with 'L', and it is only then will they find their respective brides. The duo accordingly re-locate to London, get hired with LeLe Garments, and shortly thereafter both do meet two young women, Dolly and Pooja. Problems surface when Lakshman finds out that his girlfriend, Dolly, is actually having an affair with Prem.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?379731</url></doc>
